---
// QuantumLearningPath.astro — Learning path for getting into quantum computing
---

<div class="qlp-wrap">
  <h3 class="qlp-title">Your Quantum Learning Path</h3>
  <p class="qlp-sub">From zero to building quantum circuits. No physics degree required.</p>

  <div class="qlp-path">
    <div class="qlp-step" style="--i:0;--c:#4ade80">
      <div class="qlp-level">Level 1</div>
      <div class="qlp-name">Foundations</div>
      <div class="qlp-items">
        <div class="qlp-item">Learn Python basics (if you haven't)</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Understand bits, gates, and logic</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Read "Quantum Computing: An Applied Approach"</div>
      </div>
      <div class="qlp-time">~2 weeks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="qlp-step" style="--i:1;--c:#06b6d4">
      <div class="qlp-level">Level 2</div>
      <div class="qlp-name">Quantum Basics</div>
      <div class="qlp-items">
        <div class="qlp-item">Qubits, superposition, entanglement</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Quantum gates (H, X, CNOT)</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">IBM Quantum Learning courses (free)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="qlp-time">~3 weeks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="qlp-step" style="--i:2;--c:#f59e0b">
      <div class="qlp-level">Level 3</div>
      <div class="qlp-name">Hands-On Programming</div>
      <div class="qlp-items">
        <div class="qlp-item">Install Qiskit, build circuits</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Run on simulators, then real hardware</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Implement Bell states and teleportation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="qlp-time">~4 weeks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="qlp-step" style="--i:3;--c:#a78bfa">
      <div class="qlp-level">Level 4</div>
      <div class="qlp-name">Algorithms</div>
      <div class="qlp-items">
        <div class="qlp-item">Grover's search algorithm</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Shor's factoring (conceptual)</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Variational algorithms (VQE, QAOA)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="qlp-time">~6 weeks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="qlp-step" style="--i:4;--c:#f472b6">
      <div class="qlp-level">Level 5</div>
      <div class="qlp-name">Specialization</div>
      <div class="qlp-items">
        <div class="qlp-item">Pick a domain: chemistry, finance, ML, or cryptography</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Contribute to open-source quantum projects</div>
        <div class="qlp-item">Join the Qiskit community or PennyLane ecosystem</div>
      </div>
      <div class="qlp-time">Ongoing</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .qlp-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .qlp-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 .25rem}
  .qlp-sub{color:#64748b;font-size:.78rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem;font-family:monospace}
  .qlp-path{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
  .qlp-step{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;opacity:0;animation:qlpIn .4s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(var(--i)*.12s);border-left:3px solid var(--c)}
  .qlp-level{color:var(--c);font-size:.6rem;font-family:monospace;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:.15rem}
  .qlp-name{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .qlp-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;margin-bottom:.35rem}
  .qlp-item{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.68rem;line-height:1.4;padding-left:12px;position:relative}
  .qlp-item::before{content:"→";position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--c);font-size:.6rem}
  .qlp-time{color:#475569;font-size:.58rem;font-family:monospace}
  @keyframes qlpIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}}
</style>
